## hdparm.conf — managed by Ansible (playbooks/power.yml)
## HDD spindown for RAID5 array on WD Red 3.6TB drives.
## Drives spin back up automatically on any RAID or filesystem access.

{% for dev in hdd_devices %}
{{ dev }} {
    apm = {{ hdd_apm_level }}
    spindown_time = {{ hdd_spindown_timeout }}
}

{% endfor %}
